list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: 1.Hard code for private key to authentication card. 2.Add Discover and Setting Screens 3.Add conditions to check manufacturer: - if host device Samsung stat enable alarm - else just scan only , 4. Add AlarmRecevier with flag isAlreadyCreateAlarm = true 5. In AlarmReceiver We add - AlarmWorkManager => in doWork we just logging - Rearm Alarm every 30 seconds, 6. Add MyWorkManager with flag isAlreadyCreateWorkerThread = true , 7.In doWork of MyWorkManager we do BleRecevier.startScanning, 8.When user click notification after rang we change isAlreadyCreateWorkerThread = false to do step 5 & 6 again
